reviewText:
Oh wow. Maybe you need to play more than 45 min of this tripe, but it's like the worst parts of Galaxy on Fire 2 and Freelancer put together into one, big, bad part. No hubs, no upgrades (that ♥♥♥♥ is not an upgrade, it's progression, different things). Here's how it goes:

A cutscene. Then a bit of fighting. Then a cutscene. Then some more fighting. But wait! A cutscene! And now more fighting.
